+----------------------+
|      Streamlit UI    |
|----------------------|
| - Upload documents   |
| - Enter query        |
| - Display answer & sources
+-----------+----------+
            |
            v
+----------------------+
|   Coordinator Agent  |
|----------------------|
| - Receives tasks     |
| - Sends to ingestion |
| - Sends queries to retrieval |
| - Sends results to LLM |
+-----------+----------+
            |
            v
+------------------------------+
|           Agents Layer       |
|------------------------------|
| 1. IngestionAgent            |
|    - Parses PDFs, DOCX, CSV, PPTX, TXT
|    - Chunks & cleans text
|    - Stores embeddings in FAISS
|                              |
| 2. RetrievalAgent            |
|    - Receives user query
|    - Computes query embedding
|    - Searches vector store
|    - Returns top-k relevant chunks
|                              |
| 3. LLMResponseAgent          |
|    - Builds prompt with top-k context
|    - Calls OpenAI LLM via API
|    - Sends final answer to UI
+------------------------------+
            |
            v
+------------------------------+
|      Storage Layer           |
|------------------------------|
| - VectorStore (FAISS)        |
| - Metadata store (JSON)      |
| - Sentence Transformers for embeddings
+------------------------------+
